{"title":{"en":"B. Counting Substrings","ru":"B. Подсчет подстрок"},"contestId":"269118","problemIndex":"B","timeLimit":{"en":"2 seconds","ru":"2 секунды"},"memLimit":{"en":"512 megabytes","ru":"512 мегабайт"},"inputFormat":{"en":"standard input","ru":"стандартный ввод"},"outputFormat":{"en":"standard output","ru":"стандартный вывод"},"problemHtml":{"en":"<p>Now try to modify the algorithm to solve the following problem.</p><p>Given a string $$$t$$$ and $$$n$$$ queries, each query is a string $$$s_i$$$. For each request you need to count how many times the string $$$s_i$$$ occurs as a substring in $$$t$$$. </p>","ru":"<p>Попробуйте модифицировать метод, чтобы решить следующую задачу.</p><p>Дана строка $$$t$$$ и $$$n$$$ запросов, каждый запрос — это некоторая строка $$$s_i$$$. Требуется для каждого запроса определить, сколько раз строка $$$s_i$$$ встречается в $$$t$$$ как подстрока.</p>"},"inSpecsHtml":{"en":"<div class=\"section-title\">Input</div><p>The first line of input contains the string $$$t$$$ ($$$1 \\le |t| \\le 300,000$$$).</p><p>The second line contains an integer $$$n$$$, the number of queries ($$$1 \\le n \\le 300,000$$$). The following $$$n$$$ lines contain one non-empty line $$$s_i$$$ each. The sum of the lengths of all strings $$$s_i$$$ does not exceed $$$300,000$$$.</p><p>All strings consist of lowercase English letters.</p>","ru":"<div class=\"section-title\">Входные данные</div><p>Первая строка входных данных содержит строку $$$t$$$ ($$$1 \\le |t| \\le 300,000$$$).</p><p>Вторая строка содержит целое число $$$n$$$&nbsp;— число запросов ($$$1 \\le n \\le 300,000$$$). Следующие $$$n$$$ строк содержат по одной строке $$$s_i$$$. Сумма длин всех строк $$$s_i$$$ не превосходит $$$300,000$$$. </p><p>Все строки состоят из строчных латинских букв.</p>"},"outSpecsHtml":{"en":"<div class=\"section-title\">Output</div><p>For each request print one integer, the number of times the string $$$s_i$$$ occurs as a substring in $$$t$$$. </p>","ru":"<div class=\"section-title\">Выходные данные</div><p>Для каждого запроса выведите одно число — сколько раз встречается строка $$$s_i$$$ в строке $$$t$$$. </p>"},"noteHtml":{"en":null,"ru":null},"sampleTestcases":[{"id":1642057602418,"input":"ababba\n3\nba\nbaba\nabba","output":"2\n0\n1\n","result":{"id":1642057602418,"stdout":"2\n0\n1\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":0,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642057602419,"input":"itmouniversity\n3\nit\nmore\nuniversity\n","output":"2\n0\n1\n","result":{"id":1642057602419,"stdout":"2\n0\n1\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642057602420,"input":"aaa\n2\na\naa","output":"3\n2\n","result":{"id":1642057602420,"stdout":"3\n2\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}}],"submitUrl":"https://codeforces.com/edu/course/2/lesson/2/3/practice/contest/269118/submit","language":"c++","langId":"54"}